reviewText: Do not buy!!!!! I paid alot for this cuz it's advertised as the subliminal tour but only comes with 3 videos.... It also states 10 min if you read the details which I glossed over...my fault...buy the real subliminal inside the nine dvd it's the best one!!! Has these same videos but so much more.. First dvd is Slipknot every day life and the second is videos,interviews and the concert... By far my favorite dvd of theres!!!!!!  If you're a true maggot then you definitely need for your collection
